    <h4><p>Scan</p></h4>
    <hr />
    <form method="POST" action="Pages/Scan/computerScanner.hta">
      <p>Scan the <strong>Entire Computer</strong> for viruses or malware.</p>
        <input style="min-width:125px;" type="submit" value="Computer Scan" title="Scan the entire computer for viruses or malware." alt="Scan the entire omputer for viruses or malware."></input></form>
    <form method="POST" action="Pages/Scan/diskScanner.hta">        
      <p>Scan an individual <strong>Disk Or Volume</strong> attached to this computer.</p>
        <input style="min-width:125px;" type="submit" value="Disk Scan" title="Scan a disk or volume for viruses or malware." alt="Scan a disk or volume for viruses or malware."></input></form>
    <form method="POST" action="Pages/Scan/fileScanner.hta">
      <p>Scan a <strong>Single File Or Folder</strong> on this computer for viruses or malware.</p>
        <input style="min-width:125px;" type="submit" value="File-Folder Scan" title="Scan a file for viruses or malware." alt="Scan a file for viruses or malware."></input></form>
    <form method="POST" action="Pages/Scan/remoteScanner.hta">
      <p>Scan a <strong>Remote Computer</strong> for indicators of compromise.</p>
        <input style="min-width:125px;" type="submit" value="File-Folder Scan" title="Scan a remote computer for viruses or malware." alt="Scan a remote computer for viruses or malware."></input></form>
